Key Match Events: Wiese and Erasmus hit four boundaries to score 21 runs in the Super Over
Post-Match Reflections: Wiese aged a couple of years after the emotionally draining win
Wiese stated that the pitch was two-paced and required adaptation
Wiese was disheartened that his team allowed Oman to come back into the game after dismissing them for a low target
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was a low-scoring enthralling game
It marked the first Super Over in a men's T20 World Cup tournament since 2012
